# =====================================================================
# PROPRIETARY COMPONENTS — НИКОГДА не commit'ить
# (per md_docs/12-component-split-open-vs-proprietary.md)
# =====================================================================
# Three closed-source components that must live in separate private repos.
# If they appear as subdirectories here (for local dev convenience),
# this section prevents accidental commit to the open-source core.

# Proprietary executor — two-leg trade execution engine
/arbitrage-executor/
/arbitrage-executor/**
arbitrage-executor/
**/arbitrage-executor/

/silvana-executor/
/silvana-executor/**
silvana-executor/
**/silvana-executor/

/silvana-rebalancer/
/silvana-rebalancer/**
silvana-rebalancer/
**/silvana-rebalancer/

# Proprietary rebalancer — legacy local checkout (prefer canton/silvana-rebalancer/)
/rebalancer/
/rebalancer/**
rebalancer/
**/rebalancer/

# Proprietary rebalancer — cross-venue inventory routing engine (legacy name)
/arbitrage-rebalancer/
/arbitrage-rebalancer/**
arbitrage-rebalancer/
**/arbitrage-rebalancer/

# Proprietary signer — secrets & signing vault (4th component, per upgrade-plan.md)
/arbitrage-signer/
/arbitrage-signer/**
arbitrage-signer/
**/arbitrage-signer/

# Generic safety net — anything tagged proprietary/private/closed-source
/proprietary/
/private/
/closed-source/
*.proprietary
*.proprietary.*

# Proprietary engine config / secrets / build artifacts
**/executor-config*.json
**/rebalancer-config*.json
**/cex-api-secrets*.json
**/canton-wallet*.json
**/secret_rsa_keypair*.json
**/proprietary-*.env

